examples.en: I know my strengths and weaknesses.
Be aware of your own strengths and weaknesses.
The tutor assessed the student's strengths and weaknesses.
The plan has strengths and weaknesses.
During the interview, she minimized her weaknesses and emphasized her strengths.
One of our great strengths is our ability to take it on the chin and come out fighting.
This program will teach you how to maximize your strengths while minimizing your weaknesses.
